<plot>Cachorros is a narrative short film that beautifully portrays the coming of age, and loss of innocence, when a nine-year-old son of a ranch-worker, is told to kill his newborn puppies. The super 16mm black and white film was shot in a remote farm in Argentina. In 8 minutes we go into the life of a little boy who tries to get away with not doing his task.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?090082</url></doc>
